Showmetheshell installation steps:

    git clone --recursive http://github.com/vti/showmetheshell.git
    sudo cpan -i IO::Pty Term::VT102
    cd showmetheshell
    perl showmetheshell

If non websocket aware browser is used, flash policy server must be started:

    sudo perl mojo/examples/flash-policy-server.p&

Point your browser to http://127.0.0.1:3000 (localhost doesn't work
under Chrome).

The default login and password can be found at the beginnig of the
"showmetheshell" file.
